<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> Typical intended viewing distance 
</b> 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody " valign="top"><row class="- topic/row "><entry align="left" class="- topic/entry " colname="col1" valign="top"><p class="- topic/p "> Fine details range 
