</p></entry><entry align="left" class="- topic/entry " colname="col2" valign="top"><p class="- topic/p "> Smaller POP, Fine Art, Photography, Backlit, Displays and Signs 
</p></entry><entry align="left" class="- topic/entry " colname="col3" nameend="col4" namest="col3" valign="top"><p class="- topic/p "> Up to 1 m (39.4") 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry align="left" class="- topic/entry " colname="col1" valign="top"><p class="- topic/p "> Close range - Photo 
</p></entry><entry align="left" class="- topic/entry " colname="col2" valign="top"><p class="- topic/p "> Fine Art, Photography, Interior Decoration, Small POP/POS, Backlit, Displays and Signs, Decoration 
